### Returns all push subscriptions
GET {{BASE_URL}}/push-subs
X-Tag: {{TAG}}
X-Auth-Token: {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Returns push subscription record
GET {{BASE_URL}}/push-subs/5
X-Tag: {{TAG}}
X-Auth-Token: {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Checks whether push subs exists or not
GET {{BASE_URL}}/push-subs/check/44136fa355b3678a1146ad16f7e8649e94fb4fc21fe77e8310c060f61caaff8a
X-Tag: {{TAG}}
X-Auth-Token: {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Add push subscription 
POST {{BASE_URL}}/push-subs
X-Tag: {{TAG}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-Auth-Token: {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
   "user_agent": "Mozilla/1.0",
   "payload": "{}",
   "tag": "RESTCL"
}

### Delete push subscription
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/push-subs/43
X-Tag: {{TAG}}
X-Auth-Token: {{AUTH_TOKEN}}
